{"id":"the-moons-lullaby","slug":"the-moons-lullaby","title":"The Moon's Lullaby","title_ko":"달의 자장가","level":"A2","ageBand":"8-10","coverUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/cover.webp","summary_ko":"아무도 잠들지 못하는 마을을 위해 달이 직접 부드러운 자장가를 불러 주는 포근한 이야기예요.","wordCount":107,"pages":[{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"In a small village, no one could sleep.","translation_ko":"작은 마을에서, 아무도 잠들 수 없었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"In","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":120},{"word":"a","charStart":3,"charEnd":4,"startMs":120,"endMs":320},{"word":"small","charStart":5,"charEnd":10,"startMs":320,"endMs":580},{"word":"village","charStart":11,"charEnd":18,"startMs":580,"endMs":980},{"word":"no","charStart":20,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1440},{"word":"one","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1620},{"word":"could","charStart":27,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1820},{"word":"sleep","charStart":33,"charEnd":38,"startMs":1820,"endMs":2180}]},{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"The nights were long and restless.","translation_ko":"밤은 길고 잠 못 이루는 날들이었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":220},{"word":"nights","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":220,"endMs":500},{"word":"were","charStart":11,"charEnd":15,"startMs":500,"endMs":760},{"word":"long","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":760,"endMs":1080},{"word":"and","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1460},{"word":"restless","charStart":25,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1740}]}]},{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"Babies cried, and tired parents sighed.","translation_ko":"아기들은 울고, 지친 부모들은 한숨을 쉬었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Babies","charStart":0,"charEnd":6,"startMs":0,"endMs":560},{"word":"cried","charStart":7,"charEnd":12,"startMs":560,"endMs":1040},{"word":"and","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1040,"endMs":1400},{"word":"tired","charStart":18,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1760},{"word":"parents","charStart":24,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1760,"endMs":2180},{"word":"sighed","charStart":32,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2180,"endMs":2640}]},{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"Even the owls looked sleepy.","translation_ko":"심지어 부엉이들도 졸려 보였어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Even","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":440},{"word":"the","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":440,"endMs":760},{"word":"owls","charStart":9,"charEnd":13,"startMs":760,"endMs":1200},{"word":"looked","charStart":14,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1760},{"word":"sleepy","charStart":21,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1760,"endMs":2320}]}]},{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"High above, the Moon watched the village.","translation_ko":"저 높은 곳에서, 달이 마을을 바라봤어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"High","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"above","charStart":5,"charEnd":10,"startMs":380,"endMs":760},{"word":"the","charStart":12,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1580},{"word":"Moon","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1580,"endMs":1760},{"word":"watched","charStart":21,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1760,"endMs":2140},{"word":"the","charStart":29,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2140,"endMs":2700},{"word":"village","charStart":33,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2700,"endMs":2700}]},{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p3-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"I will help them,\" she whispered.","translation_ko":"\"내가 도와줘야지.\" 달이 속삭였어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/audio/p3-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"I","charStart":1,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":180},{"word":"will","charStart":3,"charEnd":7,"startMs":180,"endMs":380},{"word":"help","charStart":8,"charEnd":12,"startMs":380,"endMs":600},{"word":"them","charStart":13,"charEnd":17,"startMs":600,"endMs":1120},{"word":"she","charStart":20,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1120,"endMs":1240},{"word":"whispered","charStart":24,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1680}]}]},{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p4","pageNo":4,"spread":"p4","imageUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/p4.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"The Moon began to sing a gentle lullaby.","translation_ko":"달이 부드러운 자장가를 부르기 시작했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/audio/p4-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"Moon","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":240,"endMs":580},{"word":"began","charStart":9,"charEnd":14,"startMs":580,"endMs":920},{"word":"to","charStart":15,"charEnd":17,"startMs":920,"endMs":1380},{"word":"sing","charStart":18,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1380,"endMs":1440},{"word":"a","charStart":23,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1740},{"word":"gentle","charStart":25,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1740,"endMs":2040},{"word":"lullaby","charStart":32,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2040,"endMs":2520}]},{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p4-s2","ord":1,"text":"Her voice was as soft as silver light.","translation_ko":"달의 목소리는 은빛처럼 부드러웠어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/audio/p4-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Her","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"voice","charStart":4,"charEnd":9,"startMs":240,"endMs":580},{"word":"was","charStart":10,"charEnd":13,"startMs":580,"endMs":820},{"word":"as","charStart":14,"charEnd":16,"startMs":820,"endMs":1380},{"word":"soft","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1380,"endMs":1380},{"word":"as","charStart":22,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1380,"endMs":1820},{"word":"silver","charStart":25,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1820,"endMs":1980},{"word":"light","charStart":32,"charEnd":37,"startMs":1980,"endMs":2360}]}]},{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/p5.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p5-s1","ord":0,"text":"The song floated down through the windows.","translation_ko":"노래는 창문을 통해 아래로 흘러내렸어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/audio/p5-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":320},{"word":"song","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":320,"endMs":760},{"word":"floated","charStart":9,"charEnd":16,"startMs":760,"endMs":1240},{"word":"down","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1760},{"word":"through","charStart":22,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1760,"endMs":2320},{"word":"the","charStart":30,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2320,"endMs":2880},{"word":"windows","charStart":34,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2880,"endMs":2880}]},{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p5-s2","ord":1,"text":"It wrapped around every bed.","translation_ko":"그 노래가 모든 침대를 포근히 감쌌어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/audio/p5-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"It","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":900,"endMs":1640},{"word":"wrapped","charStart":3,"charEnd":10,"startMs":1640,"endMs":1920},{"word":"around","charStart":11,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2280},{"word":"every","charStart":18,"charEnd":23,"startMs":2280,"endMs":2660},{"word":"bed","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":2660,"endMs":2920}]}]},{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p6","pageNo":6,"spread":"p6","imageUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/p6.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p6-s1","ord":0,"text":"One by one, the villagers closed their eyes.","translation_ko":"하나둘, 마을 사람들이 눈을 감았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/audio/p6-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"One","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"by","charStart":4,"charEnd":6,"startMs":380,"endMs":640},{"word":"one","charStart":7,"charEnd":10,"startMs":640,"endMs":880},{"word":"the","charStart":12,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1820},{"word":"villagers","charStart":16,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1820,"endMs":1820},{"word":"closed","charStart":26,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1820,"endMs":2280},{"word":"their","charStart":33,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2280,"endMs":2560},{"word":"eyes","charStart":39,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2560,"endMs":2940}]},{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p6-s2","ord":1,"text":"Their worries slowly melted away.","translation_ko":"그들의 걱정이 천천히 녹아 사라졌어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/audio/p6-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Their","charStart":0,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":440},{"word":"worries","charStart":6,"charEnd":13,"startMs":440,"endMs":980},{"word":"slowly","charStart":14,"charEnd":20,"startMs":980,"endMs":1660},{"word":"melted","charStart":21,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1660,"endMs":2080},{"word":"away","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2080,"endMs":2480}]}]},{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p7","pageNo":7,"spread":"p7","imageUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/p7.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p7-s1","ord":0,"text":"Soon the whole village was fast asleep.","translation_ko":"곧 온 마을이 깊이 잠들었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/audio/p7-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Soon","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":400},{"word":"the","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":400,"endMs":600},{"word":"whole","charStart":9,"charEnd":14,"startMs":600,"endMs":1000},{"word":"village","charStart":15,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1240},{"word":"was","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1580},{"word":"fast","charStart":27,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1580,"endMs":1920},{"word":"asleep","charStart":32,"charEnd":38,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2320}]},{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p7-s2","ord":1,"text":"Even the wind grew calm and still.","translation_ko":"바람마저 잔잔하고 고요해졌어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/audio/p7-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Even","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":280},{"word":"the","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":280,"endMs":600},{"word":"wind","charStart":9,"charEnd":13,"startMs":600,"endMs":760},{"word":"grew","charStart":14,"charEnd":18,"startMs":760,"endMs":1040},{"word":"calm","charStart":19,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1040,"endMs":1440},{"word":"and","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1820},{"word":"still","charStart":28,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1820,"endMs":2000}]}]},{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p8","pageNo":8,"spread":"p8","imageUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/p8.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p8-s1","ord":0,"text":"Every night since then, the Moon has sung.","translation_ko":"그날 밤부터 매일 밤, 달은 노래를 불러요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/audio/p8-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Every","charStart":0,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":580},{"word":"night","charStart":6,"charEnd":11,"startMs":580,"endMs":1000},{"word":"since","charStart":12,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1640},{"word":"then","charStart":18,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1640,"endMs":2020},{"word":"the","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":2460,"endMs":2620},{"word":"Moon","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2620,"endMs":2900},{"word":"has","charStart":33,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2900,"endMs":3300},{"word":"sung","charStart":37,"charEnd":41,"startMs":3300,"endMs":3560}]},{"id":"the-moons-lullaby-p8-s2","ord":1,"text":"And the village sleeps in peace.","translation_ko":"그리고 마을은 평화롭게 잠들어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-moons-lullaby/audio/p8-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"And","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"the","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":240,"endMs":840},{"word":"village","charStart":8,"charEnd":15,"startMs":840,"endMs":860},{"word":"sleeps","charStart":16,"charEnd":22,"startMs":860,"endMs":1320},{"word":"in","charStart":23,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1320,"endMs":1800},{"word":"peace","charStart":26,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1800,"endMs":2140}]}]}],"quiz":[{"question_ko":"마을 사람들에게 어떤 문제가 있었나요?","type":"mc","options":["아무도 잠들 수 없었다","먹을 것이 없었다","길을 잃었다","비가 그치지 않았다"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"밤이 길고 잠 못 이루어 아무도 잠들 수 없었어요.","id":"the-moons-lullaby-q1","ord":0},{"question_ko":"누가 마을을 돕기로 했나요?","type":"mc","options":["달","해","별","바람"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"높은 곳에서 마을을 지켜보던 달이 \"내가 도와줘야지\"라고 했어요.","id":"the-moons-lullaby-q2","ord":1},{"question_ko":"달은 마을을 어떻게 도왔나요?","type":"mc","options":["부드러운 자장가를 불러 주었다","불을 밝혀 주었다","비를 내려 주었다","바람을 불어 주었다"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"달이 은빛처럼 부드러운 목소리로 자장가를 불러 주었어요.","id":"the-moons-lullaby-q3","ord":2},{"question_ko":"자장가를 들은 마을 사람들은 어떻게 되었나요?","type":"mc","options":["걱정이 녹고 잠들었다","더 깨어 있었다","노래를 따라 불렀다","춤을 추었다"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"노래가 침대를 감싸자 걱정이 녹아 사라지고 하나둘 잠이 들었어요.","id":"the-moons-lullaby-q4","ord":3},{"question_ko":"그 뒤로 마을의 밤은 어떻게 되었나요?","type":"mc","options":["매일 밤 달이 노래해 평화롭게 잠든다","다시 잠들지 못하게 되었다","달이 사라졌다","낮에도 잠을 잤다"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"그날부터 매일 밤 달이 노래하고, 마을은 평화롭게 잠들어요.","id":"the-moons-lullaby-q5","ord":4}]}